name: Edelrid BulletProof Quickdraw
description: A bomber carabiner with a silver bullet that solves the problem of edge wear. It uses a steel insert at the point of hightest wear, where the rope contacts it on the bottom edge. The rest of the carabiner (and the top carabiner) is aluminum.Top carabiner is a straight gate Bullet carabiner.Bottom carabiner is a bent gate Bulletproof carabiner with reinforced steel insert to minimize rope friction.Durable nylon dogbone.Rope-end has anti-twist keeper to hold it in place.
